50|$|Williams {{was elected}} to the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame {{as a member of the}} <b>Platters</b> in 1990. Tony {{performed}} with his own version of the <b>Platters,</b> known as the International <b>Platters,</b> featuring his wife Helen Williams. Musical director William Gulino worked with Tony Williams and the <b>Platters</b> off and on from 1978 to 1992.|$|R
